This paper deals with natural language processing and specifically with parsing temporal dependency structures in text. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CL (Computation and Language). The paper also uses neural networks and machine learning techniques, which suggests that it could also belong to cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.LG (Machine Learning). Additionally, the paper mentions that it evaluates its parser on two domains, news reports and narrative stories, which suggests that it could also belong to cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) and cs.IR (Information Retrieval).
